        content_en: "<p>Female circumcision can affect pregnancy, childbirth and subsequent problems. Special follow-up during pregnancy and childbirth may be necessary. Complications can include problems with urination, menstruation and intercourse. Specialized health care is available for women who have been subjected to circumcision.</p>",
